**Steps to Reproduce**:

1. Have code like the following:

    ```c#
    abstract class B<T>
    {
        public abstract T? M();
    }

    class D : B<int>
    {
    }
    ```
2. Use <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>.</kbd> to select "implement abstract class".

**Expected Behavior**:

This generates code that compiles, i.e.:

```c#
public override int M()
{
    throw new NotImplementedException();
